Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.10,0:00:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.42,0:00:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(181,348)\fnImpact\fax-0.5\fscy200\fscx150\fs38\shad0\1c&H282E80&\3c&HC0C0C0&\3a&HD0&\b1}Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.45,0:00:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Set Up! Set Up! Set Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Gin no kamen ni kuro mafuraa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A mask of silver and a black muffler
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hitai ni kagayaku Bui to Bui
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,V and V shining on his forehead
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}「Sutoppu! Goddo no waru-dakumi」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,"Stop GOD's conspiracy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.00,0:00:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no sakebi wa nami no oto
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.00,0:00:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,His father's scream is the sound of the waves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.80,0:00:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ikari no Raidoru hikinuite
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.80,0:00:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Furiously drawing the Ridol
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.86,0:00:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu Raidaa kyou mo yuku
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.90,0:00:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider comes again today
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.20,0:00:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X! X! X!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.50,0:01:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Killed with his father by the evil organisation GOD,\NJin Keisuke is revived as Kamen Rider X.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.80,0:01:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,His mission: to preserve peace and justice by\Nfighting the mysterious agency known as GOD.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.99,0:01:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,'I Want Bloood'\NThe Leech Monster of Corpse Swamp!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.00,0:01:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Pitiful humans! GOD rules\Nthis world, you'll see!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.80,0:01:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Die! Die, humans! Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.70,0:02:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Come, my darling pet!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.00,0:02:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Drink your fill of young maidens' blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.10,0:02:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Die! Die, humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.50,0:02:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Good news, your temperature's gone down!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.60,0:02:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But you shouldn't be moving around yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.70,0:02:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so bored!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.80,0:02:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A l-leech!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.10,0:03:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.20,0:03:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,There was... a scary old\Nlady... at the window!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.20,0:03:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.00,0:03:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not kidding! She was\Nfrowning at me, all creepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.60,0:03:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.90,0:03:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What a silly thing to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.50,0:03:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,For one thing, we're three floors up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.40,0:03:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,How could anyone be at the window?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.40,0:03:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just a little delirious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.50,0:03:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, you need rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.50,0:03:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Young lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.90,0:04:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't I read your fortune?\NIt's free! Come, sit down!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.20,0:04:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,How old are you, my dear?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.10,0:04:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Eighteen...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.30,0:04:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So young!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.40,0:04:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, pick a card...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.40,0:04:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,A leech...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.40,0:04:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Not just any leech! They\Nfeed on human blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.10,0:04:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,...and they look just like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.80,0:04:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Monster!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.50,0:04:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Go now, and drink your fill of that girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.50,0:05:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that a scream...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.40,0:05:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure I heard something...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.40,0:05:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show you, Jin Keisuke...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.60,0:06:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, drink her blood too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.00,0:06:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Michiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.70,0:06:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong, Michiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.10,0:06:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Michiko...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.90,0:06:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you offer your\Nblood to my darling pet!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.60,0:07:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The chief said he didn't\Nwant you getting bored, Chiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.90,0:07:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.90,0:07:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe some music'll help you rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.20,0:07:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-Well, I'd better be going.\N-See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.50,0:07:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait... You're mistaken to think\Nyou're unbeatable, Jin Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.10,0:07:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,GOD...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.50,0:07:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.70,0:07:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.20,0:07:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.50,0:07:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We want bloood!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.70,0:07:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We must drink blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.40,0:07:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-We want your blood!\N-Are you three crazy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.20,0:08:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We want bloood!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.20,0:08:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Those girls have had their blood\Ndrained by the blood-sucking leech!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.70,0:08:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Now they must wander\Nin search of new blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.30,0:08:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the heck are you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.20,0:08:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.50,0:08:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Pitiful humans! GOD rules this\Nworld, you'll see! Die! Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.30,0:09:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.40,0:09:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Leech Dracula, inheritor\Nof Count Dracula's blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.30,0:09:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Give your blood to\Nmy leeches and die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.60,0:09:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Leech Dracula's leeches\Ncan melt human flesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.60,0:09:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Die, Jin Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.50,0:10:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,My leeches, melt Jin Keisuke's body!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.60,0:10:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Great Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.10,0:10:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Try this, X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.60,0:11:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The real terror is yet to begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.50,0:11:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Leech Dracula, how is your plan progressing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.30,0:11:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir! Just wait and see\Nwhat horrors I unleash next!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.30,0:11:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody help me!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.20,0:11:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to drink your blood! Your blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.80,0:11:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,L-leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.10,0:11:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Your blood! Give it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.70,0:11:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! I need your blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.40,0:11:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Is anyone there!? Someone help!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.30,0:12:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Blood...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.20,0:12:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.60,0:12:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.50,0:12:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me... drink your blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.50,0:12:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Help! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.80,0:12:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-Please save us!\N-Vampires!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.80,0:12:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,-H-hurry, quickly!\N-Boss!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.90,0:12:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Say what!? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.00,0:12:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-Chief?\N-Keisuke! There are vampires at Chiko's hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.60,0:13:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Blast... So that's what Leech Dracula meant!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.20,0:13:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about, Keisuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.40,0:13:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-th-the TV!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.60,0:13:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A leech!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.40,0:13:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Tachibana Toubei! Jin Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.90,0:13:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are, GOD monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.90,0:13:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who have had their blood drained will\Nhungrily seek out the blood of others!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.70,0:13:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokyo is now a hive of vampires!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.90,0:13:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you after?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.60,0:13:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Deliver your pieces of the\NRS Device's blueprints to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.50,0:13:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You expect me to\Ngive you the blueprints?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.10,0:14:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It is the only way to cure the vampires!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.30,0:14:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I will await you at the banks of Corpse Swamp...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.40,0:14:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiko! You've gotta save Chiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.60,0:14:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief, check out the hospital.\NMake sure Chiko's safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.10,0:14:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.30,0:14:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'm going to Corpse Swamp.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.00,0:14:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you're--!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.50,0:14:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't let anyone else become a vampire.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.40,0:14:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.60,0:15:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Jin Keisuke shall die! He shall\Ndie here in Corpse Swamp!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.40,0:15:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-There you are, Jin Keisuke!\N-I kept my word.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.00,0:15:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you have the blueprint pieces?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.80,0:15:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.50,0:15:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,All five of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.30,0:15:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hand them over!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.20,0:15:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The genuine article!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.70,0:15:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,With that, I'll take my leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.40,0:15:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And what about the vampires?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.10,0:15:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really think I care?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.60,0:16:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.70,0:16:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Corpse Swamp is bottomless! Once\Nyou go down, you don't come up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.70,0:16:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Writhe in pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.70,0:16:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Leech Dracula, you've truly proven\Nyourself by eliminating Jin Keisuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.20,0:16:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, King Dark, those bloodthirsty\Nhumans will take care of the rest...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.20,0:17:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-I want blood!\N-Give me blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.50,0:17:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-Give me blood!\N-I want blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.50,0:17:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-Chiko!?\N-Boss!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.40,0:17:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-I want blood!\N-I want blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.90,0:17:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I want blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.60,0:17:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I want bloood!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.40,0:17:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-I want blood!\N-I want blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.80,0:18:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-My body's melting!\N-The pain...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.10,0:18:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-Boss?\N-Alright, we beat them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.70,0:18:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.70,0:18:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it! It was the salt\Nyou threw at them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.30,0:18:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-Salt?\N-Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.10,0:18:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! Leeches can't stand salt!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.40,0:18:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-We've gotta get to Corpse Swamp and tell Keisuke!\N-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.60,0:18:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,King Dark, the blueprints.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.10,0:18:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent work! Your peers in the\NVillain Army could learn a lot from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.60,0:19:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Dracula's descendant has no 'peers'!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.40,0:19:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,W-what's this!? Look at those blueprints!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.50,0:19:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I-impossible! They were there a minute ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.60,0:19:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Imbecile!! They obviously\Nused disappearing ink!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.20,0:19:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Deal with Jin Keisuke properly\Nthis time, Leech Dracula!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.40,0:19:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse that Jin Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.80,0:19:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you drowned already, Jin Keisuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.90,0:19:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Great Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.60,0:20:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.40,0:20:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The salt brought by Tachibana Toubei\Nmelts Leech Dracula's leeches!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.10,0:20:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,My leeches are melting!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.80,0:20:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a quick one!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.50,0:20:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never live down bringing\Nthose fake blueprints back! Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.60,0:22:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Vacuum Hell Wheel!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.40,0:22:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The Vacuum Hell Wheel is a deadly finishing move that reduces\Nthe enemy's offensive power by rolling them through the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.20,0:22:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, they're finished with an X Kick.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.70,0:22:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hell Wheel Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.10,0:22:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Accursed X Rider! Next time,\Nwe'll send him to hell itself!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.40,0:23:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Leech Dracula's vampire plan has been foiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.20,0:23:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But King Dark will use any means to get those\Nfive blueprint pieces. Fight on, X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.30,0:23:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(462,420)\fad(0,850)\fs38}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.10,0:23:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(194,72)\fs38}Next episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.70,0:23:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,In search of the rest of the RS Device's blueprints,\NLizard Viking targets a young girl in the Nasu Highlands.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.30,0:23:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course, the courageous Kamen\NRider X takes a stand against him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.69,0:23:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, look forward to GOD and X Rider's battle for the\N blueprints in Nasu Highlands:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.43,0:23:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,"Arise! King Dark!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.10,0:23:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ore wa Ekkusu Ekkusu Raidaa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.10,0:23:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I am X, X Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.77,0:23:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no tsukutta Kaizoogu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.77,0:23:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,A Kaizorg created by my father
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.65,0:23:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Tetsu yori tsuyoi
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.65,0:23:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Stronger than iron
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.74,0:23:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oto yori hayai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.74,0:23:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Faster than sound
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.87,0:23:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu masuku paafekutaa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.87,0:23:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,X's mask, Perfecter
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.04,0:23:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no negai ga ore no chi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.04,0:23:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,My father's wishes are in my blood
